            "content": "<p>You can subscribe to Tonique on the Site. Our subscription program works like this:</p><ul><li><strong>Commitment level:</strong> Subscriptions are available at the 30/month level (two 15-packs at $2.99 per pouch, $89.70 per month) and the 60/month level (four 15-packs at $2.74 per pouch, $164.40 per month). A single 15-pack is sold as a one-off purchase only.</li><li><strong>Auto-renewal:</strong> Your subscription renews automatically at the cadence and price you selected, using the payment method on file, until you cancel. We’ll send you a reminder email before each shipment so nothing arrives as a surprise.</li><li><strong>Skipping, pausing, and cancelling:</strong> You can skip a shipment, pause your subscription, or cancel at any time from your account page. Changes need to be made before your next renewal date to apply to that shipment. There are no cancellation fees.</li><li><strong>Price changes:</strong> If we change subscription pricing, we’ll let you know at least 30 days before the change takes effect, so you can decide whether to stay subscribed.</li></ul><p>*Legal review note: Auto-renewal terms must comply with California’s Automatic Renewal Law (ARL) and similar state statutes. Confirm that the checkout flow includes (1) clear and conspicuous disclosure of renewal terms, (2) affirmative consent before charging, (3) post-purchase acknowledgment with cancellation instructions, and (4) an easy online cancellation method. The bullet list above reflects these obligations but the implementation needs to match.</p>"
